Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里，我们将学习如何区分向量。并按比例\NHere, we will learn to distinguish between vectors. And scale as
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,向量是同时具有一个数量级和一个数字的对象\Nvectors are objects that have both a magnitude, a single number
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还有方向，\Nand direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,而比例尺只有一个量级。\Nwhereas scale as have only a magnitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们看看每个例子。\NLet's see some examples of each.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,某物的长度是标量，\NThe length of something is a scalar,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.59,0:00:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这只是数量级，\Nbecause it's just the magnitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,拉力某人拉动某物所施加的力量\Na force exerted by someone pulling something
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是一个向量，\Nis a vector,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们关心力量的力量，\Nbecause we care about the strength of the force,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,大小，\Nthe magnitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,以及力的作用方向\Nand the direction in which the forces acting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,温度。\Ntemperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个定标器。\NIt's a scaler.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们在天气图上显示温度，\NIf we display temperature on a weather map,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在空间中每个点的温度值不同的地方，\Nwhere the value of the temperature is different at each point in space,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个标量场\Nthis is a scalar field
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.34,0:00:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,相比之下。\Nin comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这张风的天气图，\NThis weather map of wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,或者空间中每个点的风速值，\Nor the value of the wind velocity at each point in space,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.73,0:00:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,由矢量表示\Nis represented by a vector
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:00:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是一个向量场。\Nis a vector field.
